{
  "texts": [
    "Credibility aimed to ensure accuracy and trust in the investigation, with the researchers faithfully representing the diverse perspectives provided by the interviewees.",
    "This commitment to credibility was reinforced through crosschecking to validate the findings of the study.",
    "Transferability addresses the applicability of the study's conclusions to diverse settings beyond higher education and the specific Chatbot under examination.",
    "This involved a focus on potential extrapolation, and required a comprehensive presentation of the research process and assumptions to facilitate broader relevance.",
    "Dependability underscored transparency in the research process, striving to enhance reliability and providing a framework for the results to be replicated in similar studies."
  ]
}